<paragraph id="79085C0259665813588EC584F8F45752" blockId="5.[174,1233,1428,1711]" pageId="5" pageNumber="322">
This species prefers the mountain and foothill regions, it develops in 
<taxonomicName id="BEB72781596658135C66C585FDF854B3" box="[1035,1232,1460,1486]" pageId="5" pageNumber="322">
<emphasis id="4BC38010596658135C66C585FD5F54B3" box="[1035,1143,1461,1486]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="322">Trametes</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
